{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":233,"createTime":"2019-06-03 10:16:38","topicId":null,"tagId":39,"rule":4,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p style=\"line-height:24px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">发热</span></strong></p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、病因诱因：有无受凉、创伤?</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、主要症状特点：热度、病程、性质（持续性还是间断性）、发热规律（稽留热还是驰张热）、持续时间、加重或缓解因素？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、伴随症状：有无寒战、结膜充血、淋巴肿大、肝脾肿大、出血、昏迷？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、全身状态：发病以来饮食、睡眠、大小便及体重变化。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、诊疗经过：发病以来是否到医院检查过，曾做过哪些检查和治疗、治疗是否有效？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、相关病史：(1)有无药物过敏史、手术史</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">(2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与该病有关的其他病史，既往有无类似发作，有无糖尿病、结核病、妇科病或服用免疫抑制剂病史，有无烟酒嗜好，有无肿瘤病家族史，女性患者月经史、不洁性交。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"","topic":null,"options":[],"tags":[{"id":279,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 16:02:40","updateTime":"2019-06-01 16:02:40","name":"发热","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":19},{"id":39,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 13:42:53","updateTime":"2019-06-01 13:42:53","name":"发热","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":15}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}